CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
Department of Cabinet Affairs (Mantrimandal Karya Vibhag)
New Delhi, 26 March, 1977.
5 Chaltra, 1399 (s).
In continuation of this Department Memo. of
even number dated the 24th March, 1977, the undersigned
is directed to say that the Members of the Council of
Ministers shown in the attached list were sworn in
by the Acting President at 9-30 A.M. today, the 26th
March, 1977.
